OL,4,Cdifficult year, says new CEO
OL,6,FLeaders of the have been facing
OL,7,Fquestions from Members on the Culture
OL,8,Fand Sport Committee following a
OL,9,Fdamning review of the WRU published
OL,10,Flast November which revealed a
OL,11,Fwidespread culture of misogyny and
OL,12,Fsexism.
OL,14,FAmong some of the evidence included in
OL,15,Fthat report was that a WRU
OL,16,Frepresentative had expressed views
OL,17,Fthat 'men are the master race' and how
OL,18,Fthere was gossip about how a female
OL,19,Fmanager had 'slept her way' to a job.
