OL,4,Cdifficult year, says new CEO
OL,6,FOther information revealed how slurs
OL,7,Fabout women in same sex relationships
OL,8,Fwere thrown around the organisation.
OL,10,FThere has been significant change in
OL,11,Fthe way the is run. A new board has
OL,12,Fbeen established and Abi Tierney has
OL,13,Ftaken over as Chief Executive Officer.
OL,15,FAsked how she summarised staff morale
OL,16,Fas someone who has joined relatively
OL,17,Frecently she said that "if I can use a
OL,18,Ffew words to describe what I've seen
OL,19,Fand felt, I think 'hope' is one of
OL,20,Fthem.
