OL,6,FShe said: "I think people are really
OL,7,Fhopeful that the changes ... and the
OL,8,Freview that we've gone through will
OL,9,Fenable them to draw a line and move
OL,10,Fforward in a really positive way. So
OL,11,Fthere's a real sense of hope and
OL,12,Flooking forward.
OL,14,F"But I think that is balanced with a
OL,15,Freal sense of tiredness and they went
OL,16,Fthrough a lot last year."
