OL,6,FChair Richard Collier-Keywood told the
OL,7,Fmembers, "I think that we have learnt
OL,8,Ffrom what we've both read in the
OL,9,Freport and what we have heard as we've
OL,10,Ftalked to different members of staff."
OL,12,FHe also said that all the members of
OL,13,Fthe new board "are absolutely
OL,14,Fcommitted to seeing a new culture,
OL,15,Fboth in the WRU itself and in the
OL,16,Fclubs and on the field in terms of
OL,17,Fwhere we play rugby."
