OL,6,FAlso giving evidence to the committee,
OL,7,FNigel Walker, who's Executive Director
OL,8,Fof Rugby at the and who stood in as
OL,9,Finterim CEO during the crisis said
OL,10,Fthat the main mistake leaders had made
OL,11,Fpreviously was not to realise how
OL,12,Fwidespread the toxic culture was.
OL,14,FHe acknowledged that "the union had
OL,15,Ffailed to join the dots. There were a
OL,16,Fnumber of individual incidents and
OL,17,Fthey remained as individual incidents,
OL,18,Fand we didn't bring them together.
