OL,3,CWRU staff 'hopeful' but 'tired' after
OL,4,Cdifficult year, says new CEO
OL,6,F"I think when you've had - and what
OL,7,Fhappened 12 months ago was more than a
OL,8,Fwarning - when you have a television
OL,9,Fprogramme, which lays bare the ills of
OL,10,Fan organisation all in 30 minutes, you
OL,11,Fwill be rather foolish not to take
OL,12,Fheed and to sense-check that the
OL,13,Fchanges which have been made in the
OL,14,Fprevious 12 months ... just to sense-
OL,15,Fcheck that the things that went wrong
OL,16,Fbefore could not happen again.
