OL,3,CWRU staff 'hopeful' but 'tired' after
OL,4,Cdifficult year, says new CEO
OL,6,F"And then there are many things that
OL,7,Fwe have done: a whistleblowing
OL,8,Fhelpline, giving our staff more
OL,9,Fconfidence in being able to speak up
OL,10,Fand us demonstrating that we're
OL,11,Fprepared to listen - there are a whole
OL,12,Fraft of things.
OL,14,F"But I think to bring it down to one
OL,15,Fthing, it was not joining the dots
OL,16,Fwhen there were a series of incidents
OL,17,Fover a period of time ... and not
OL,18,Fbringing those things together and
OL,19,Fsaying we've got a problem here. How
OL,20,Fcan we address that problem?"
